{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"67127e493a","title":"“肃反中被斗的人起来争人权”","origin":"北京地质勘探学院党委会宣传部编《社会主义教育参考资料第二编：右派言论汇编》，1957年10月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"066570ca8e","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"67127e493a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"82cc012e26","name":"北京地质勘探学院"},{"id":"8320407b5d","name":"沈启明"},{"id":"aedf5a9ea9","name":"曾荫浓"},{"id":"cd6d1d2c70","name":"李燕吉"},{"id":"ec445d94b0","name":"蔡荣荣"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bfe0f89b68","type":"title","text":"“肃反中被斗的人起来争人权”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67127e493a"},{"id":"472ab325f9","type":"authors","text":"北京地质勘探学院沈启明李燕吉蔡荣荣曾荫浓","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67127e493a"},{"id":"fcef23bcd2","type":"paragraph","text":"沈启明说：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67127e493a"},{"id":"6ea708982e","type":"paragraph","text":"「肃反中被斗的人起来争人权，争自由，争民主。」","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67127e493a"},{"id":"65e9259fb4","type":"paragraph","text":"李燕吉说：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67127e493a"},{"id":"53e569d25d","type":"paragraph","text":"「肃反侵犯了人权，丧失了人的自尊心，现在应该维护人的尊严。肃反扩大化了，错误很大，成绩不多，尤其是地质学院。肃反不应该搞思想批判，肃反是组织整人，尤其是天津人整的最多，这是偏见。」","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67127e493a"},{"id":"a74c171a28","type":"paragraph","text":"蔡荣荣说：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67127e493a"},{"id":"79d24c82e2","type":"paragraph","text":"「在我们堂堂的最高学府里，竟发生私设刑堂，打人，这严重的违反了国家法律，难道这不能说我们在肃反问题上的错误是严重的吗？」","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67127e493a"},{"id":"b9a88a9ba5","type":"paragraph","text":"「肃反我没有参加过，但情况我想不会好多少，这种情况不仅严重地违反宪法，也违犯了众所公认的人道精神。不仅不能容忍的，也是严重地违法的。我希望从今以后，人权与人道能得到进一步的保障。」","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67127e493a"},{"id":"fb2faa4b26","type":"paragraph","text":"曾荫浓说：","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67127e493a"},{"id":"91046c7193","type":"paragraph","text":"「我院肃反是私设刑堂，非法逼供，违犯宪法，是惨无人道，成绩是主要的，错误是次要的简直是教条，肃反那怕肃错一个也是肃民。」「肃反的错误起肃民的作用。」","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67127e493a"}],"page":{"id":"c44cfd96ea","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67127e493a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}